casebody.data:
Jane DOE
v.
WAKE COUNTY, et al. No. 137P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2019 J. Locke Milholland, IV, Attorney at Law, for Doe, Jane. Roger A. Askew, Senior Deputy County Attorney, Mary Boyce Wells, Senior Assistant County Attorney, Brian Kettner, Assistant County Attorney, for Wake County, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 16th of April 2019 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of June 2019."
